<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在哪里？”罗西大声叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>幽灵强盗就在这个房间里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是罗西不知道他到底在哪儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西突然听到跑步的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她转身看到一扇门很快地打开，又很快关上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在那儿！”罗西从钱堆上跳了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她打开门，冲进长长的走廊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个坏人的脚步声拐了一个弯儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跟过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她在拐弯的时候，她看到另一扇门打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！罗西用眼睛发射激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！门被炸开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！你看不见我！”幽灵强盗笑着继续跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西站住，仔细听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能听见他的脚步声。”她想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他正在另一个走廊上跑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跟在后面，边听边走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>脚步声到了另一个大房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这间房墙边有一台巨大的机器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>机器上有大型滚轮和传送带。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>纸币铺满了传送带。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106333</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁边还有几桶墨水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这一定是工人印钞票的地方。”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐！突然，一个垃圾桶砸在罗西旁边的墙壁上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”幽灵强盗喊道，“没打中！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到另一个垃圾桶飞在空中，然后砸向自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在垃圾桶砸到自己之前，罗西躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>垃圾箱砸在机器上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西赶紧飞过去，想要抓住强盗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈！你永远抓不到我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>强盗说完，就安静了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>用自己的超级听力，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西听到那个坏蛋的心跳声就在附近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她向声音飞过去，想要抓住幽灵强盗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，她再次错过了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>幽灵强盗大笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每次罗西听到声音，都会飞过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，每次幽灵强盗都躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"啊！”罗西跺着脚，墙壁摇晃起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果他是隐形的，我永远都阻止不了这个大坏蛋！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我真是受够了！啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个箱子击中罗西，把她撞倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她碰到了一桶墨水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>墨水溅到她的靴子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看着墨水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”她想，“我有办法了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跳起来，举起一桶墨水，洒向空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼！罗西把墨水吹得满屋都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>墨水洒到墙壁上，机器上，还有幽灵强盗的身上！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哈！”罗西喊道，“我现在能看见你了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>